- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with image classification and feature extraction using deep learning for breast cancer histology images. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper discusses the use of transfer learning and multi-view learning to improve classification performance. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper uses deep learning techniques to analyze medical images. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with feature extraction and classification of images. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a less likely category, but possible as the paper deals with the analysis of medical images.
